tips.title: Emoji Picker in Windows
tips.description: Did you know that Windows now includes an emoji picker? To open the emoji picker you can press Windows + . (period) key. Pressing Windows + ; (semicolon) will also open the emoji picker. To insert the emojis, place the cursor in a text field in any app and then click on the emoji of your choice.

tips.title: FindTime
tips.description: Did you know that you can use 'FindTime' (an Outlook add-in) to help you schedule meetings? FindTime makes use of polls to determine the best dates and times for all invitees and creates the meeting for you.

tips.title: Journal your achievements
tips.description: Creating yourself a daily journal and complete this each day. Include 3 things you were grateful for and 3 things you were able to accomplish each day.
